{"word":"Corn","slug":"corn","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Corn</b> A general term applied to all grains.<br/> In valleys<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=65&verse=13'>Psa 65:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=4&verse=28'>Mar 4:28</a><br/> A product of Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=49'>Gen 41:49</a><br/> A product of Palestine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=33&verse=28'>Deu 33:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=27&verse=17'>Eze 27:17</a><br/> Parched<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=2&verse=14'>Rth 2:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=17'>1Sa 17:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=25&verse=18'>1Sa 25:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=28'>2Sa 17:28</a><br/> Ground<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=19'>2Sa 17:19</a><br/> Eaten by the Israelites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=5&verse=12'>Jos 5:12</a><br/> Shocks of, burnt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=15&verse=5'>Jdg 15:5</a><br/> Heads of, plucked by Christ's disciples<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=12&verse=1'>Mat 12:1</a><br/> Mosiac laws concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=22&verse=6'>Exo 22:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=23&verse=25'>Deu 23:25</a><br/> Figurative<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=72&verse=16'>Psa 72:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=14&verse=7'>Hos 14:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=12&verse=24'>Joh 12:24</a><br/> Symbolic<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=5'>Gen 41:5</a><br/><a href='S:Barley'>Barley</a>; <a href='S:Barn'>Barn</a>; <a href='S:Bread'>Bread</a>; <a href='S:First Fruits'>First Fruits</a>; <a href='S:Gleaning'>Gleaning</a>; <a href='S:Harvest'>Harvest</a>; <a href='S:Reaping'>Reaping</a>; <a href='S:Rye'>Rye</a>; <a href='S:Threshing'>Threshing</a>; <a href='S:Tithes'>Tithes</a>; <a href='S:Wheat'>Wheat</a>"}]}